    "description": "The FarmGTEx TWAS-server is a web-based platform that allows users to perform transcriptome-wide association studies (TWAS) across tissues and species, leveraging gene expression data from human, pig, and cattle. It supports various analyses including gene expression prediction, GWAS imputation, and functional annotation.",
